title: Maureen O'Hara, spirited movie star, dies at 95
text: > Entertainment Maureen O'Hara, spirited movie star, dies at 95 FILE - This Oct. 27,1950 file photo shows Maureen O'Hara signs autographs for school children of Moab, Utah, while on location there for a new film. O'Hara,who appeared in such classic films as "The Quiet Man” and How Green Was My Valley," has died. Her manager says O’Hara died in her sleep Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015 at her home in Boise, Idaho. (AP Photo/Frank Filan, File)
